<td><div align="center">符合条件的记录共有<%=recordnum%>条，本页显示<%=intOffset%>―<%if intOffset+intPage-1 > recordnum then response.write recordnum else response.write intOffset+intPage-1 end if%>条，共<%=pagenum%>页</div></td>
</tr>
</table>
